    bibo:volume "5174" ;
    dc:creator "Babenko, Anatoly; Shveenkova, Yulia; Potapov, Mikhail" ;
    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "New species of the genus Philotella Najt & Weiner, 1985 (Collembola, Neanuridae, Pseudachorutinae) from the Russian Far East" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986748>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986752>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986754>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986758>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986760> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986748>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56–61. Key characters of Philotella: 56–58, Th. II in P. cedrina sp. nov. (56), P. oligotricha sp. nov. (57), and P. japonica (58, after Tamura, 1988); 59–60, Abd. I in P. caeca sp. nov. (59) and P. cedrina sp. nov. (60); 61, tip of leg III in P. amurica sp. nov. (inner side)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986748/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986752>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62–65. Key characters of Philotella: 62–63, Th. II in P. obesa (62, after Babenko, 2007) and P. pallida sp. nov. (63), 64–65, Abd. I in P. obesa (64, after Babenko, 2007) and P. caeca sp. nov. (65)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986752/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986754>
    dc:description "FIGURES 66–71. Key characters of Philotella: 66–67, PAO in P. cf. obesa (66) and P. caeca sp. nov. (67); 68–71, Abd. II and Abd. IV in P. miracli (68, 70, after Najt & Weiner, 1985) and P. amurica sp. nov. (69, 71)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986754/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986758>
    dc:description "FIGURES 72–78. Key characters of Philotella: 72–73, labium in P. pax sp. nov. (72) and P. aliniensis sp. nov. (73); 74–75, labrum in P. cedrina sp. nov. (74) and P.pax sp. nov. (75); 76–77, Abd.III and IV in P. cedrina sp. nov. (76) and P. pax sp. nov. (77); 78, Abd. IV in P. alba sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986758/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986760>
    dc:description "FIGURES 79–82. Key characters of Philotella: 79–80, Th. II in P. porcella (79, after Fjellberg, 1985) and P. oligotricha sp. nov. (80); 81–82, Abd. IV–V in P. deharvengi (81, after Najt & Weiner, 1985) and P. tertia (82, after Najt & Weiner, 1985)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986760/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

